flowchart TD
    A([Admin opens user security actions]) --> B[Select Force logout]
    B --> C[Optionally enter reason]
    C --> D{Permission and tenant scope valid?}
    D -- No --> E[Show permission denied]
    D -- Yes --> F[Confirm action]
    F --> G[System revokes every target session]
    G --> H[Target is signed out on all devices]
    H --> I[Admin sees revoked-session count]
    I --> J([Audit record stored])
